oiSteps to install CocoaPods

1.) Install "Command line tools" from preferences of Xcode
2.) Go to terminal and execute below code
3.) sudo gem update --system
4.) sudo gem install cocoapods
5.) go to directory of your project in terminal
6.) execute : touch Podfile
7.) Open Podfile in text editor  and write below code 

platform :ios,'5.0'

pod 'project name','project version'

8.) save and exit this file
9.) go to terminal (directory set to your project)
10.) pod install 
11.) close your demo.xcodeproj
12.) open workspace file

Thats it,
